Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:30.44,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to where
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:32.11,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I once belonged, BUT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:35.98,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振り向けば 風の音だけ　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:37.24,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let me down　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:38.74,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me confuse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:43.87,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望が塗り潰してく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:45.70,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Escape from here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:47.53,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:50.17,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追いかけてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:53.89,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢も　理想も　情熱も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:57.42,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,またかき消されて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:23:00.47,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哀しい日々は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:04.06,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつかは終わりが来るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:06.90,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷いながら　もがきながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:12.88,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それでも　まだあきらめたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:14.82,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷だらけでも　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:19.82,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この手のひらに 決して消えない星がある 　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:23.17,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流れて堕ちた光は今も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:26.95,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの場所を遠く照らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.24,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何度でも手を伸ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:33.42,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今は描けなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:36.53,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じることが強さに変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:40.07,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝いてよ　Shooting STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:30.44,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to where
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:32.11,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I once belonged, BUT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:35.98,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转身遥望 只有风声　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:37.24,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let me down　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:38.74,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me confuse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:43.87,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将绝望掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:45.70,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Escape from here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:47.53,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:50.17,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:53.89,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想　理想　热情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:57.42,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也全都消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:23:00.47,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:04.06,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会有结束之日？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:06.90,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惘着 挣扎着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:12.88,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 也还不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:14.82,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:19.82,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在手中 仍有绝不会消失的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:23.17,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑落之后 那光芒现在也 　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:26.95,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然远远地照耀着那里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.24,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数次伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:33.42,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使现在无法描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:36.53,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任会化为力量
